Looks like a tooth.

41:12.887 --> 41:14.707
Jug...

41:14.710 --> 41:16.189
Baby Teeth.

41:17.675 --> 41:20.343
Or what's left of him.

41:20.345 --> 41:23.694
Terry, I'm getting close
to the clearing that the...

